{"tid":1525051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 睇吓黑警點跳黨鐵閘","createTime":"2019-08-31T19:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T09:31:13.000Z","uid":199926,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"03afc0940874682dc71118da81791bf514e5b511","tid":1525051,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43YEMWF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43YEMWF.png&h=b4a2487d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1JoheM22grs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1JoheM22grs&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=8671b915\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1JoheM22grs</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39eb6ba7a394617f3f58eef6d0410dea2c33695e","tid":1525051,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:22:45.000Z","msg":"學到野"},{"pid":"568fb7cb783c3e029f1fdb286bce8b2815f48dab","tid":1525051,"uid":160102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:23:43.000Z","msg":"喂屌你老母，知法犯法喎"},{"pid":"36959fabbb0099c49847fc275df13e1a2df5faa5","tid":1525051,"uid":228934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:23:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當年有份聯署既人，大部分都走哂，仲留得係度既人，你都估到佢係咩人？？有人性嘅，應該一早 劈炮，唔再做 cctvb吧！但係佢仲要做足7年，做到2019 年今日，然後佢想洗白拎光環，叫3毛 錢7開post造勢，想拎光環夾橫行直入海關警察入境. 繼續染紅政府為藍屍發聲。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我心裡梗係想佢係因良心發現而辭職啦<br />\n佢係鬼良心發現辭職咩<br />\n係比班同事投訴佢番工唔做野掛住化妝<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">覺得比人杯先辭渣<br />\n仲帶哂光環咁<br />\n屋企警察世家攞咩光環</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後 cctvb假新聞記者主播無一個無辜 <br />\n唔好亂信任何消息 為佢哋洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警 主播 死 全 家"},{"pid":"abf1bd6c1eb67b5d91e6aa3668f8fa3639c8173e","tid":1525051,"uid":63117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:26:18.000Z","msg":"學下野啦手足<br />\n今日仲見到有人用八仔出站 <br />\n知唔知你地咁做幾危險"},{"pid":"ec7a05a41d1bd03472c9d5759e6fb2fa090fba54","tid":1525051,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:28:00.000Z","msg":"暴徒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768b0c4580ba79a32d999f0e6fd71a5169e9c20c","tid":1525051,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:30:02.000Z","msg":"堆"},{"pid":"a02260f187ded8d1ecd9994acea39788289450cd","tid":1525051,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:34:05.000Z","msg":"阿sir跳閘唔使你教"},{"pid":"ae034f29b3cfff4fb90def05500e939f4dcacfd4","tid":1525051,"uid":238716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:36:55.000Z","msg":"記者會話警務人員執法時係守法㗎，姐係跳閘都係守法㗎喇"},{"pid":"8de627423b7d8143178f39e4b3b0b3af4fddc123","tid":1525051,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:37:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8b990489842249a1c70aa5b57b98e6ac38bc1b7","tid":1525051,"uid":26106,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:37:44.000Z","msg":"啊sir仆街呀"},{"pid":"2db88af56c9690fbabc7cd8d5e92155ed1c9d2d9","tid":1525051,"uid":276911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:38:07.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"f08d06b2c1645a0125ee0cd87b16494fc7c0e717","tid":1525051,"uid":51495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:41:31.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a77a14babf16428295bb99cf1e26ddd1fa73201","tid":1525051,"uid":52271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:41:43.000Z","msg":"查飛狗邊敢埋去"},{"pid":"42bd6ba48e8ee913be820e61e9e2e95e